verbose_text: The ENG subdermal contraceptive implant is a device consisting of 68 mg of ENG as the active ingredient with an average release rate of 60-70 mug / day in weeks 5-6, decreasing to ~ 35-45 mug / day by the end of the first year, 30-40 mug / day by year 2, and then to 25-30 mug / day at the end of the third year.
evidence: decreasing to ~35-45 mug/day by the end of the first year, 30-40 mug/day by year 2, and then to 25-30 mug/day at the end
